{"type": "article", "id": 50028, "title": "这个倒着放的儿童屋，可能会让你这个大人看很久｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-07T23:26:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47648, "name": "Müller Möbelwerkstätten"}, {"id": 47649, "name": "Studio Michael Hilgers"}, {"id": 47650, "name": "I Love Handles"}, {"id": 47651, "name": "Ilsangisang"}, {"id": 23565, "name": "Fogia"}, {"id": 8925, "name": "Moooi"}, {"id": 47652, "name": "Alma-nac"}, {"id": 8928, "name": "Luca Nichetto"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 164, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180207220315NDM9fm2d6zB4Jl3E.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: #657ab7} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s7 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s8 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s9 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s10 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Upside Down House by Alma-nac</h3><p>一个色彩丰富的房子倒过来，变成了一个攀爬架，这是出自建筑设计事务所 Alma-nac 的主意。它将于今年夏天建成，成为英国雷丁一个居民区绿园村新的儿童游乐园的一部分。亮点包括与窗户相连的攀岩墙，围绕着彩绘栅栏的阳台和隐藏在窗户后的隧道。</p><p>“这个简单的概念带来了一个全新的世界，” Alma-nac 表示。“地板变成了天空，屋顶变成了地板，从烟囱进入，滑出了前门。”曾有人提出，儿童游戏空间的设计往往缺乏想象力。然而，Alma-nac 的游戏屋是对传统游戏空间的创造性反思。这个设计的目的是对该地区的房屋进行抽象化、俏皮化地再创造，鼓励孩子们以新的方式看待周围的环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220355qlC3fYLIODv21NX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.601946\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220356kT7tcefjPFKgy38v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566836\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220356MZW1EruxG3DvRgq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220356IlKqcjJQnoYb6iZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770305\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220357Hz0exGYvXT3VM2K1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220357KbZ8PDa5SdLJcvo4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/02/06/alma-nac-upside-down-house-build-uk-play-park-architecture-reading-berkshire-england/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Canal Chair by Luca Nichetto for Moooi</h3><p>意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 为荷兰设计品牌 Moooi 设计了这款运河椅（Canal Chair），灵感来自于中古世纪的欧洲战船，这种船型在地中海水道上占据主导地位数百年。椅子的背部看起来就像是船头，搭配大胆的配色组合。椅子的基座样式不一，甚至还有旋转基座，意在适配各种室内设计环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802072204501dHYWthEelsik9Z3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499707\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802072204508uiFMa5lqe0m6Nyh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220450fh0jNEaCKQqJ3sDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666800\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220451okPE36HmgyCsiqpn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666800\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>2018 Collection for Fogia</h3><p>在本周的斯德哥尔摩设计周上，瑞典家具品牌 Fogia 推出了 2018 系列家具，色彩丰富和厚重的面料感是其特色。意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 设计的一套棕色调陶瓷餐具，以及 Stefan Borselius 设计的棕色皮革座椅，融合了斯堪的纳维亚的简约主义风格和 1970 年代的形式和色彩。其他亮点包括一套几何软垫蒲团，一个边桌和配有圆形细节的搁架单元，以及一系列图案地毯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220530aTPYWcDRs9XtLq1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749577\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802072205318bWVC4qAXtGy0Pra.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220531NEi8sCl4jQuykR1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220531A0kaPWf8JQ4YTEeG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.255922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220533jUrW5TewQt73N2zP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>斯德哥尔摩的<a href=\"http://notedesignstudio.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Note Design Studio</a> 为该系列设计了一款陶瓷品，一个类似拉伸织物的玻璃吊灯，以及一个巨大的橡木桌，意在向日本的木工制品致敬。</p><p>该系列中的其他椅子包括由丹麦工作室 Norm Architects 设计的带木腿的休闲椅，以及 Andreas Engesvik 设计的 Bollo 椅的新版本，这把椅子已成为 Fogia 最具辨识度的产品之一。</p><p>瑞士设计二人组 <a href=\"http://www.diiis.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Diiis</a> 创造了小型 Hawu 搁架单元和 Gito 边桌等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220623FykeK1HUEnftZQV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.204738\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220623fQSYBFLHEITVCjhR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.374365\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802072206242lOBTgeWiu365sn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220624YzAqmPidVaB83XtW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220624WT12XcCFxYlHJBt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/02/06/fogia-furniture-collection-stock-holm-design-week-pays-homage-1970s-stockholm-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Light Shelf by Ilsangisang</h3><p>首尔设计工作室 Ilsangisang 最近推出了一款灯光搁架，继续探索以灯具为主题的各种设计可能性。Light Shelf 的底座试图模仿光束的形状，既可以放在桌上使用，也可以挂置在墙壁上。不同的放置方法，也决定了其究竟是作为置物架还是便签板。设计师希望为用户提供打开台灯后光线聚焦的视觉效果，充满趣味性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220657oLFizIlvbB3c9Z5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220657tRTE8A5GoiYyuOqW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220657oGUiHQVYchDAbP4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220657Jiuzd4IYC1sF3Wql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802072206586BY4Ds0QvCfJ1rGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802072206584RprVD3NLMWHqtyO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Depeche Node by I Love Handles </h3><p>I Love Handles 是一家专注于制造苹果产品配件的公司，Node 是其最新推出的多功能充电设备。如果你有一个iPad Pro，你可能也有一个 Apple Pencil。如果你想同时给它们充电，你需要两根充电线。如果你有这两种设备，你可能还会有一个 iPhone。你怎么一次充三个设备？</p><p>Node 是一个解决方案，它是一款采用十字结构的 Lighting 集线器，在给两台 Lighting 设备充电的同时，另一侧的母口还可以接入 Apple Pencil 。售价 19.95 美元，<a href=\"https://ilovehandles.com/shop/node/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220747pCznytGSrsHhOYkU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559724\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220748YherztZ42DoqIvLK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559753\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220748oTwjFKcYx7pnr5lU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559753\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220748oPAQps9lxuSKC1RN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559561\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220748AHVIblPO2yJC6Uae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559561\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Twofold Space Saving Wall Shelf/Desk Hybrid by Studio Michael Hilgers for Müller Möbelwerkstätten</h3><p>意大利设计品牌 Müller Möbelwerkstätten 推出了一款紧凑的壁挂式书架，出自设计工作室 Studio Michael Hilgers 之手。它同时也可以作为书桌。</p><p>实木制成的架子，将顶部向下翻转，则可以伸展为一个工作台。当处于工作台模式时，原有书架上的书籍和物品会保留在远处，同时为用户提供充足的工作空间。完成后，将其旋转上翻，便又能恢复到书架状态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220814E5tKzkjuNsiApqX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220814iOJMbS6aP4zNxYVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.945313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220814PJCVr4BSyb7EHXgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220814dHVMqEcSkQplLAy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.553906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220815N1VZMTKG28SyUQa7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180207220816SRdEcQHOeIyhLzkP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777778\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}